---
import tabghaLogo from '/img/logo-peces-pan.png'
import tabghaLogoOLD from '/img/tabgha-logo.png'
import RestaurantSVG from './icons/Restaurant.astro'
import ArrowRightSM from './icons/ArrowRightSM.astro'
---

<section class="relative md:pt-0 bg-tabgha-beach bg-cover bg-left sm:bg-center bg-no-repeat lg:mb-20 md:mb-16">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/0 to-black/0 sm:bg-transparent sm:bg-gradient-to-r sm:from-black/0 sm:to-black/0"></div>

    <div class="relative text-black mx-auto max-w-screen-xl md:py-32 py-20 px-6 sm:flex sm:flex-row-reverse md:h-screen sm:items-center lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-xl text-center justify-center sm:bg-opacity-60 bg-opacity-90 p-12 rounded-xl bg-white">
            <img src={tabghaLogoOLD} alt="Tabgha Logo" class="p-6 m-auto">
            <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold sm:text-5xl ">TABGHA
                <strong class="font-tg-title block font-extrabold text-tg-one ">
                    Portals Nous
                </strong>
            </h1>

            <p class="mt-4 max-w-lg sm:text-xl sm:leading-relaxed">
                Chiringuito en la playa de Portals Nous, Mallorca. Con una cocina mediterránea y un ambiente relajado y familiar.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-8 flex items-center flex-wrap gap-4 text-center justify-center">
                <a
                    href="#menu"
                    class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full rounded bg-tg-one bg-opacity-80 px-12 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white shadow focus:outline-none focus:ring sm:w-auto"
                >
                    <RestaurantSVG/>
                    Nuestra carta
                </a>

                <a
                    href="#sense"
                    class="flex items-center justify-center gap-2 w-full rounded bg-white px-12 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-black shadow focus:outline-none focus:ring sm:w-auto"
                >
                    Saber más
                    <ArrowRightSM/>
                </a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
